It's probably not feasible to review all the operators implemented, but I'd appreciate if important changes made to NDArray, executor and kvstore are reviewed. Any help is appreciated!

@cjolivier01 I think rtol takes the value range into consideration already. The `allclose` function tests for:
```
absolute(a - b) <= (atol + rtol * absolute(b))
```

@lxn2 first place to look at to decide the atol/rtol would be in the failed tests. It should print out the values of the largest differences. You can use them to guide the decision on atol/rtol, if you believe the implementation and tests are correct.
